International Business Machines Corp To Acquire Tealeaf Technology, Inc

Wednesday, 2 May 2012 12:05pm EDT

International Business Machines Corp announced a definitive agreement to acquire Tealeaf Technology, Inc., a provider of customer experience analytics software that helps organizations to gain intelligence and react more swiftly to consumer trends in digitally transformed marketplace. Financial details were not disclosed. The acquisition is subject to customary closing conditions and regulatory clearance and is expected to close in the second quarter of 2012.Â 

